{"tid":247204,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[求好心巴絲]跌咗手機","createTime":"2017-05-17T15:15:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-18T09:18:21.000Z","uid":46400,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"defb9c8ae5375fdb1fab41bb2278f3d8ddbd6b1b","tid":247204,"uid":46400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T15:15:56.000Z","msg":"我代我朋友開post <br />\n佢尋日(5月16日)晏就(2-3點個陣)係坐東涌去大澳架巴士(11號)落車個陣跌咗電話<br />\n佢不停打電話 都響但無人聽<br />\n打去電話公司查返 最後開機係夜晚7點58分<br />\n但睇返佢whatsapp 最後上線係夜晚9點23分<br />\n估計係有人執咗部電話<br />\n無論點都好 希望有心人執到比返部電話佢 或者比返張miscro SD卡佢 因為佢隻貓貓啱啱過生 入面有哂佢嘅遺照係度 好有紀念價值<br />\n如果有有心人比返佢 會薄酬 會高過放返部機嘅價位<br />\n電話型號: samsung j5 prime <br />\n顏色:正面白色 背面金色<br />\n(有機套 機套上係一堆合照)<br />\n麻煩大家幫手share下 唔該哂"},{"pid":"cd382c7b536a04773f690f2f24a01cb951a32c39","tid":247204,"uid":46400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T15:19:42.000Z","msg":"如有有心人拾獲 請電61385170"},{"pid":"738cb4a66451be1a74236422ecfe807b43c02a3f","tid":247204,"uid":46400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T15:35:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3561657decf6090ee0832b4e2763e61b43f2fdb","tid":247204,"uid":46400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T15:39:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16cd9de141d38b703c4a5ed12c4b06650ccb91bf","tid":247204,"uid":46400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T16:45:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"002fc8827179143d59a33e3fdd683d350bfb6b1b","tid":247204,"uid"